	<title>Bases Numéricas</title>
    
    <p>Para inserir números em uma certa base numérica use <link xref="superscript"> subscription numbers </link>. Os números seguintes são equivalentes.</p>
    <example>
    <p>
    1001011₂
    </p>    
    <p>
    113₈
    </p>
    <p>
    75
    </p>
    <p>
    4B₁₆
    </p>
    </example>
    <p>Quando no <link xref="mouse"> modo programador</link> há botões para binários(<keyseq><key>Ctrl</key><key>B</key></keyseq>),octal(<keyseq><key>Ctrl</key><key>O</key></keyseq>) e hexadecimal(<keyseq><key>Ctrl</key><key>H</key></keyseq>).</p>
    <p>
    To set the base that results are shown in change the <link xref="number-display">result format</link>.
    </p>
    <p>
    To change the base of the current result use a base button or <keyseq><key>Ctrl</key><key>D</key></keyseq> to show in decimal form.
    </p>
